<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<FrameLayout
    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="#F1F6F9"
    tools:context=".fragments.lesson8.OverviewFragment">

    <androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView
        android:overScrollMode="never"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent">
        <LinearLayout
            android:orientation="vertical"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="match_parent"
                android:orientation="vertical">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:orientation="vertical">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                        android:gravity="center_vertical"
                        android:text="Solving Routine or Non-Routine Problems Involving Addition and Subtraction of Decimals and Mixed Decimals Using Appropriate Problem Solving Strategies and Tools"
                        android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Large"
                        android:textColor="@color/black" />

                    <Button
                        android:id="@+id/btn_tts"
                        android:text="Read Aloud"
                        android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                        android:background="@drawable/btn_secondary_button"
                        android:drawableStart="@drawable/ic_text_to_speech"
                        android:textAllCaps="false"
                        android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                        android:paddingStart="10dp"
                        android:paddingEnd="20dp"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="48dp" />
                </LinearLayout>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/description_1"
                    android:text="Decimal can be defined as a whole number whose fractional part is separated by a decimal point. The digits following the decimal point show a value smaller than one."
                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                <ImageView
                    android:id="@+id/example_1"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:contentDescription="example"
                    android:layout_marginVertical="10dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/lesson_8_sample_1" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/description_2"
                    android:text="To add and subtract decimals is not too different to add and subtract any numbers. It is very important that you write your decimals so that the decimal points align, or you will find yourself adding tenths to ones or subtracting hundredths from tenths.\n\nBe sure that when adding or subtracting decimal numbers, they must have the same number of decimal places."
                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/description_3"
                    android:text="Example of adding and subtracting decimals and mixed decimals through ten thousandths without and with regrouping, and explain each step.\n\nExample: Add and Subtract Decimals\n\nAddition without Regrouping:\nAdd: 2.345 + 1.678\nSolution:\nAlign the decimal points and add each place value together:\n2.345\n+ 1.678\n-------\n4.023\n\nThe sum of 2.345 and 1.678 is 4.023.\n\nAddition with Regrouping:\nAdd: 3.857 + 2.924\nSolution:\nAlign the decimal points and add each place value together:\n3.857\n+ 2.924\n-------\n6.781\n\nThe sum of 3.857 and 2.924 is 6.781.\n\nSubtraction without Regrouping:\nSubtract: 8.456 - 3.211\nSolution:\nAlign the decimal points and subtract each place value:\n8.456\n- 3.211\n-------\n5.245\n\nThe difference between 8.456 and 3.211 is 5.245.\n\nSubtraction with Regrouping:\nSubtract: 6.548 - 3.992\nSolution:\nAlign the decimal points and subtract each place value:\n6.548\n- 3.992\n-------\n2.556\n\nThe difference between 6.548 and 3.992 is 2.556.\n\nExample: Add and Subtract Mixed Decimals\n\nAddition without Regrouping:\nAdd: 4.215 + 2.5\nSolution:\nAdd the whole numbers separately and add the decimals separately:\n4 + 2 = 6\n0.215 + 0.5 = 0.715\n----------------------\n6.715\n\nThe sum of 4.215 and 2.5 is 6.715.\n\nAddition with Regrouping:\nAdd: 6.999 + 3.201\nSolution:\nAdd the whole numbers separately and add the decimals separately:\n6 + 3 = 9\n0.999 + 0.201 = 1.200\n----------------------\n9.200\n\nThe sum of 6.999 and 3.201 is 9.200.\n\nSubtraction without Regrouping:\nSubtract: 9.812 - 3.4\nSolution:\nSubtract the whole numbers separately and subtract the decimals separately:\n9 - 3 = 6\n0.812 - 0.4 = 0.412\n----------------------\n6.412\n\nThe difference between 9.812 and 3.4 is 6.412.\n\nSubtraction with Regrouping:\nSubtract: 8.599 - 6.111\nSolution:\nSubtract the whole numbers separately and subtract the decimals separately:\n8 - 6 = 2\n0.599 - 0.111 = 0.488\n----------------------\n2.488\n\nThe difference between 8.599 and 6.111 is 2.488.\n\nWhen adding and subtracting decimals, it is essential to line up the decimal points and perform the operations column by column. Take care to regroup (borrow or carry) when necessary to maintain accuracy. Practice these examples to strengthen your skills with adding and subtracting decimals and mixed decimals through ten thousandths.\n\n"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
            </LinearLayout>

            <LinearLayout
                android:orientation="vertical"
                android:padding="16dp"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                    app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"
                    app:cardElevation="0dp"
                    app:cardBackgroundColor="#ffffff"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent">
                    <LinearLayout
                        android:orientation="vertical"
                        android:background="@drawable/bg_gradient_tutorial"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent">
                        <TextView
                            android:text="Tutorial"
                            android:textSize="18sp"
                            android:paddingTop="10dp"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <TextView
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:text="Are you struggling with the numbers mixing in your head? In this tutorial, we will guide you through the step-by-step process of this lesson!"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <Button
                            android:id="@+id/btn_tutorial"
                            android:text="Watch Tutorial"
                            android:textAllCaps="false"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:background="@drawable/btn_secondary_button"
                            android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_width="150dp"
                            android:layout_height="48dp"/>
                    </LinearLayout>
                </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
                <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                    app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"
                    app:cardElevation="0dp"
                    app:cardBackgroundColor="#ffffff"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                    <LinearLayout
                        android:orientation="vertical"
                        android:background="@drawable/bg_gradient_quiz"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent">
                        <TextView
                            android:text="Quiz"
                            android:textSize="18sp"
                            android:paddingTop="10dp"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:textColor="@color/white"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="horizontal"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                            <ImageView
                                android:layout_gravity="center"
                                android:background="@drawable/bg_list"
                                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="vertical"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="10"
                                    android:textSize="18sp"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="Multiple Choice Questions"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            </LinearLayout>
                        </LinearLayout>
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="horizontal"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                            <ImageView
                                android:layout_gravity="center"
                                android:background="@drawable/bg_clock"
                                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="vertical"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="2 mins"
                                    android:textSize="18sp"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="Per Questions"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            </LinearLayout>
                        </LinearLayout>
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="horizontal"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                            <ImageView
                                android:layout_gravity="center"
                                android:background="@drawable/bg_trophy"
                                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="vertical"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="50%"
                                    android:textSize="18sp"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="To Passed the Quiz"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            </LinearLayout>
                        </LinearLayout>
                        <TextView
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:text="Let's measure your problem-solving skills to assess your level of understanding."
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:textColor="@color/white"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <Button
                            android:id="@+id/btn_start_quiz"
                            android:text="Start Quiz!"
                            android:textAllCaps="false"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:textColor="@color/white"
                            android:background="@drawable/btn_primary_button"
                            android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_width="150dp"
                            android:layout_height="48dp"/>
                    </LinearLayout>
                </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
            </LinearLayout>
        </LinearLayout>
    </androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView>
</FrameLayout>